; Test def directive via general_directive
; Exercise the def keyword (alias for define) through the switch

def myfunc(x) = x * 2

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    (myfunc($5.00))
    Assets:Cash

test reg --limit "account =~ /Food/"
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
end test
